A cross-section of a ripe mango floating in mid-air against a deep navy background, rendered in Studio Ghibli animation style with soft, warm lighting. The fruit is cut to reveal its golden flesh in an anatomical diagram fashion, with delicate flowing ribbons of XML-like structured patterns emerging from within, transforming into organized layers that spiral outward like pages of an ancient manuscript. The ribbons shift from organic orange and yellow near the fruit to subtle blue-green geometric patterns as they extend outward. Tiny sparkles and floating seeds drift through the composition. The overall mood is one of magical transformation and hidden inner structure being revealed, with the characteristic Ghibli soft gradients and painterly texture throughout.
